description: This file declares the external API functions for the HTTP message parser component in the Cisco-based system, including creation, removal, object enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: AnscCreateHttpMPComponent
methods.description: Creates an instance of the HTTP message parser component using provided container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: AnscHttpMPCOCreate
methods.description: Creates an HTTP message parser object in the context of given container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: AnscHttpMPCORemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up the HTTP message parser object.

methods.name: AnscHttpMPCOEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the HTTP message parser instance.

methods.name: AnscHttpMPCOInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the HTTP message parser object.
